<h3>arrowShape</h3>

<p>Draws the shape of the arrows in the previous &amp; next buttons.</p>

<p>The arrow is drawn on a 100 &times; 100 viewbox with four points (<i>p0, p1, p2, p3</i>) made up of six coordinates <code>x0, x1, y1, x2, y2, x3</code>. The four points draw the top half on the left arrow.</p>

{{> arrow-wiz}}

<p>Set a custom shape by setting <code>arrowShape</code> to a <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/d">SVG path string</a>. The path is for the left arrow drawn in a 100 &times; 100 viewbox.</p>

